Title: Directs the department of labor to conduct a study on the employment rate of the Black and Latinx transgender persons in New York state
Summary: Directs the department of labor to conduct a study on the employment rate of Black and Latinx transgender persons in New York state and to make recommendations relating to the same.
ActClause: AN ACT directing the department of labor to conduct a study on the employment rate of Black and Latinx transgender persons in New York state
